Usage: setSelectedStripBoxState [-help] <index> {ROUTED FIXED COVER SHIELD}
                                [<shield_net>]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<index>                         # which selected strip box state needs to be
                                # set (string, required)
{ROUTED FIXED COVER SHIELD}     # state of the selected strip box
                                # (enum, required)
<shield_net>                    # if value is SHIELD, shield net needs to be
                                # set (string, optional)